### ============================================================================
### INVOICES — /api/v1/invoices
### ============================================================================

### List my invoices (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/invoices?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get invoice by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/invoices/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Download invoice PDF
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/pdf
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create invoice
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50000,
  "currency": "NGN",
  "description": "Professional Plan — Monthly subscription",
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "companyId": {{companyId}},
  "status": "PENDING"
}

### Update invoice
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/invoices/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 55000,
  "description": "Professional Plan — Monthly subscription (updated)",
  "status": "PENDING"
}

### Delete invoice
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/invoices/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
